### Test Riot API Integration
### This file can be used with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3111/api
@riotUsername = YourGameName#TagLine
@authToken = YOUR_SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Test League of Legends Last Match (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/riot/league/last-match?riotUsername={{riotUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test Valorant Last Match (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/riot/valorant/last-match?riotUsername={{riotUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test League of Legends with path parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/riot/league/last-match/{{riotUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test Valorant with path parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/riot/valorant/last-match/{{riotUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test with region parameter (League)
GET {{baseUrl}}/riot/league/last-match?riotUsername={{riotUsername}}&region=americas
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test with region parameter (Valorant)
GET {{baseUrl}}/riot/valorant/last-match?riotUsername={{riotUsername}}&region=na
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

